{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"91f20de93d","title":"中央批转河北省委关于队干部参加公共食堂的规定","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"56d891c998","index":0,"year":1960,"month":3,"day":7,"articleId":"91f20de93d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"e34ee12043","type":"title","text":"中央批转河北省委关于队干部参加公共食堂的规定","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"91f20de93d"},{"id":"5a6128534e","type":"appellation","text":"各省、市、自治区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"91f20de93d"},{"id":"3229fd846b","type":"paragraph","text":"河北省委关于队干部参加公共食堂的三项规定，转发给你们。这个规定很好，各地可以仿效。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"91f20de93d"},{"id":"b01b0d078b","type":"paragraph","text":" 中    央一九六○年三月七日","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"91f20de93d"},{"id":"94cc10124b","type":"appellation","text":"附件：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"91f20de93d"},{"id":"25a02206ec","type":"subtitle","text":"河北省委关于队干部参加公共食堂的规定","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"91f20de93d"},{"id":"6a9647ec76","type":"subtitle","text":"一九六○年三月一日","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"91f20de93d"},{"id":"98fb768d14","type":"paragraph","text":"为了进一步巩固和发展农村公共食堂，省委特作如下规定：","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"91f20de93d"},{"id":"c9b3cf9a05","type":"paragraph","text":"一、所有农村支部书记和队干部，除因病等特殊情况以外，一律参加公共食堂，不得单独立灶起伙。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"91f20de93d"},{"id":"2f5968a7a6","type":"paragraph","text":"二、所有参加公共食堂的干部必须同社员群众一样，按照定额吃，不得单立小灶额外吃好的。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"91f20de93d"},{"id":"4ed25cdb21","type":"paragraph","text":"三、所有到农村工作的各级干部，必须到公共食堂去吃饭。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"91f20de93d"},{"id":"f1b5c2fd5a","type":"paragraph","text":"以上规定要经过动员教育使其自觉地去认真执行，如果经过教育仍有无故拒不执行者，要给予纪律处分。","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"91f20de93d"},{"id":"ebfcb2ef6b","type":"paragraph","text":"已发：各省市委、自治区党委，政治局、书记处各同志，中央各部委，国家机关和人民团体各党组。共印一、○八一份。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"91f20de93d"},{"id":"d928cdb012","type":"paragraph","text":"来源：中共中央办公厅机要室             一九六○年三月八日发出","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"91f20de93d"}],"page":{"id":"4d08d5c98b","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"91f20de93d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}